testSteps.description: Given I want to buy items using "Mfr. Part No"
When I enter "CSCAK/1" in to search box
Then I should only see item with "Mfr. Part No" and "CSCAK/1"
Given I want to buy items using "RS Stock No"
When I enter "537-5488" in to search box
Then I should only see item with "RS Stock No" and "537-5488"
